side 
Game: Operation Flashpoint (1.00) 
Description: Returns the side of a unit or object. 
Once dead, a unit will be on the civilian side. Query the side of the Group 
 to get a reliable result. 
When used in conjunction with a format statement (hint format["%1",side 
 player]), the returned strings are: "WEST", "EAST", "GUER", "CIV", "LOGIC 
", "ENEMY" (eg: renegades), "AMBIENT LIFE" or "UNKNOWN". 
Syntax:  
 Side = side unitName 
Parameters: 
unitName: Object or Group 
Return Value: 
 Side